embeds.description:
Welcome to the chat area for the Los Angeles Section VES Members!

This channel _is_ accessible by all VES members from all sections.  Feel free to use your individual Section's channel to network with locals, plan, brainstorm, etc. or post in other channels to reach out and work with members of other sections.

Please drop suggestions or feature requests in the #suggestions channel below. We'll add additional Section channels as needed/requested.
